<h1 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:22px;color:#1a1a2e;">Confirm your new email address</h1>
<p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
<p>You have requested to change your email address. Please confirm the new address:</p>
<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:24px 0;">
  <tr>
    <td style="background-color:#1a1a2e;border-radius:6px;padding:12px 28px;">
      <a href="{{{confirmUrl}}}" style="color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;">Confirm New Email</a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p style="color:#868e96;font-size:13px;">This link is valid for {{expiresIn}}. If you did not request this change, please contact our support immediately.</p>
